<p>Dave Hamilton and John F. Braun are two of the leading experts on all things Mac (and beyond), and listeners from around the world listen to &mdash; and rely on &mdash; them to help solve their tech problems. Take a listen to today&rsquo;s Mac Geek Gab to understand exactly why &mdash; these guys are true experts who know how to translate their knowledge into easy-to-understand terms just for you. Download the show to your iPod and take John and Dave along on a car ride (virtually, of course!) and you&rsquo;ll understand why so many others do the same.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="center" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.macobserver.com/imgs/dave/macGeekGab02.jpg?resize=230%2C230" border="0" width="230" height="230" /></p>
